      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row683600#s2",
      "text": "Easily    upset and wanting to go home but  can be distracted and calmed- not    escalating over day- psych said to re-eval pt capacity if does escalate    and medicate with Haldol and distraction tactics and re-consult if pt    condition changes."
    },
    {
